<p class="general_text">
    The Social Urinal is a (semi-comical) experiment testing the boundaries of the social graph. A public urinal that
    uses face recognition to identify a "user" and send statistical information regarding their performance to facebook.
    i.e: <b> "Tomer Weller has urinated 50cc at GeekCon using the Social Urinal". </b>
</p>
