<p class="general_text">
    The Social Urinal was built at GeekCon 2012. GeekCon is an annual weekend long gathering in Israel. It gathers
    technically oriented creative talented people to think, create and deploy ideas.
</p>

<p class="general_text">
    The Social Urinal is a front to back webapp which uses Chrome's latest <a
            href="http://developer.chrome.com/apps/serial.html">"Serial"</a> interface to read data directly
    from a connected arduino micro-controller without requiring proprietary drivers or native software.
    <br/>
    <br/>
    Facebook has rejected our proposed "Urination" open graph object :)
</p>

